sub_title: Global Cognitive Supply Chain Manager IBM
summary:
Spare Part Management :

- Optimize Global Supply Chain processes
- Initiate inventory management projects
- Life cycle analysis
- Forecast optimization
- Predictive analytics
- Score Card reporting
- KPI driven operations
- Last Time Buy Calculation
- E2E Parts Planning
- Location and Hub planning
- Service improvement projects
- Install base oriented planning process
- Commodity Based planning techniques
- Planning system set up and optimization
- Executive monthly reporting/presentation
- Surplus reduction management
- Lead time reduction projects

Procurement :

- Spend analysis
- Category management
- Supplier Development programs
- Automated RFI/RFQ process
- Automated Supplier sourcing programs
- Kraljic oriented purchasing
- Online auctioning
- MSU purchasing methodology
- Complex contract implementation
- Total Cost of Ownership
- Savings projects

* Lean Six Sigma Black Belt
* NEVI Inkoop 1 & 2
* CPIM
